Usage: provide cli interface together information and status
Lun show {options} 
	- P (pool) show luns in a particular pool
	- M show mapped LUNs
-- portal
	Show all luns in a single portal
	
Lun create 
	Creates a lun in the specified pool
		Includes creating rbd
Lun map
	Maps an existing rbd to a set of initiators.  Must specify lun id
Lun unmap
Lun offline (?)
Lun destroy
